Little_Rock.East End Methodist Episcopal Church: The East End Methodist Episcopal Church (East Washington Avenue Methodist Church ; Damascus Spiritual Church) is a historic church at 2401 E. Washington Avenue in North Little Rock, Arkansas. It is a single-story brick structure, with a broad gable roof and a porch extending across part of its front facade. It was built in 1922 for a congregation founded in 1915, and is a fine local example of vernacular Craftsman architecture.
